<p>We at Networks 360 are always on the lookout for creative, diligent, hardworking folks to join our team.  Interested? Send you resume to <b>hr@networks360.net</b></p>
<br>
<h4>Job openings:</h4>

<ul class="accordion">
							<li class="accordion-item">
							<div class="accordion-switch">
								<span class="togglegfx"></span>Sales Representative
							</div>
							<div class="accordion-content">
<h6>Overview</h6>								<ul class="single-project-list">
<p>If you love sales and competition, and you enjoy dealing with different personalities and not afraid of calling business owners and presenting great services. We need to talk, we are looking for self-motivated people to act as Sales Consultants. You will be the first point of contact with our customers and you will build strong customer relationships. Your goal is to increase company sales.</p>

<h6>Responsibilities</h6>

<li><span></span>Meet sales goals by selling our services to new customers</li>
<li><span></span>Effectively present services to potential clients and follow up for sales closing</li>
<li><span></span>Handle all administrative aspects of the sale including: Sales contracts, answering questions, and filing the completed orders</li>
<li><span></span>Stay up to date with services offered knowledge, pricing plans, promotions, and other features through continuous learning and self-development</li>
<li><span></span>Keep up with the market by monitoring other offers and be able to provide market feedback to the Sales Manager regarding local competition</li>
<li><span></span>Attend networking events and exchange, present and mingle with other business people</li>
<br><br><br><br><br><br><br>
<h6>Requirements</h6>

<li><span></span>High school diploma or equivalent, some college would be preferred</li>
<li><span></span>Minimum of 1 year of IT services sales or equivalent sales in technology sector</li>
<li><span></span>Positive, can-do attitude, highly motivated, results driven, and likes to make money</li> 
<li><span></span>Great customer service skills and ability to implement company’s sales process</li>
<li><span></span>Strong presentation and communication skills</li>
<li><span></span>Organized and focused on success</li>

<br><br><br><br><br><br><br>
<p>Networks 360 is an IT solutions provider in the Houston area, with great potential for the right candidate. This is a salaried and commission job with potential that may earn you up to $100k. Company will provide business cards, cell phone, laptop, training, leads, marketing material and an office environment, with no cap on commission.</p>

<p>To apply send you resume to hr@networks360.net</p>






							</div></ul>


<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>
									





				




					 
